[2]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/util/Arrays.html#asList(T...)
[3]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/util/List.html#addAll(java.util.Collection)
[4]: https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/17/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/Stream.html#flatMap(java.util.function.Function)
